# Test simulation without ETHDebug info or ABI files
# REQUIRES: soldb
# RUN: %soldb simulate %{contract_address} "memoryTest()" --from 0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266 --rpc-url %{rpc_url} 2>&1 | FileCheck %s

# CHECK: Connecting to RPC:
# CHECK: No ABI files found. Proceeding with function signature: memoryTest()
# CHECK: Function Call Trace:
# CHECK: Status: SUCCESS
# CHECK: #1 memoryTest()
